title: WESTCOAST / MORELL barks
description: Morell checks to see if Gary is doing something useful.

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""Gary, what are you doing there?""
Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""How about rekindling that camp fir..."
dialogueTree.english: "How about rekindling that camp fire so we can dry off?"
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Можа, распаліш агонь, каб мы маглі высахнуць?»

dialogueTree.title: Morell, the Cryptozoologist: ""Don't you remember that method I s..."
dialogueTree.english: "Don't you remember that method I showed you back in... never mind."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie pamiętasz, jak cię uczyłem, kiedy... ech, nieważne”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Не памятаеш, як я цябе вучыў, калі... эх, няважна».
